##API Documentation

##Base URL:
http://<your-gcp-ip>:5002

Endpoint 1: Get Time for a City
  URL: /api/time/<city>
  Method: GET
  Description: Returns the local time and UTC offset for the given city.
URL Parameters:
  city (required): The name of the capital city (e.g., London, Paris).
  Headers:
    Authorization: Bearer token for access. Example: Authorization: Bearer supersecrettoken123
Response:
{
  "city": "London",
  "local_time": "2025-04-21 22:10:56",
  "utc_offset": 1.0
}
Errors:
401 Unauthorized: If the authorization token is missing or incorrect.
404 Not Found: If the city is not found in the database.
